<Placemark><name>B531/2026 | SRI LANKA | 03-16T19:44Z</name><styleUrl>#s</styleUrl><description><![CDATA[B0531/26 NOTAMR B0073/26 Q) MMFR/QRDCA/IV/BO/W/000/999/ A) MMFO B) 2603161944 C) 2606150500 E) THE GOVERNMENT OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA HAS ISSUED AN ADVISORY    REGARDING A POTENTIALLY HAZARDOUS SITUATION WITHIN THE MAZATLAN    OCEANIC (MMFO), MEXICO (MMFR), CENTRAL AMERICA (MHTG) , BOGOTA (SKED) ,    GUAYAQUIL (SEFG), AND PANAMA (MPZL) FLIGHT INFORMATION REGIONS.        IT IS RECOMMENDED THAT OPERATORS EXERCISE CAUTION WHILE OPERATING IN    THE AREAS OVER THE PACIFIC OCEAN AND THE GULF OF CALIFORNIA WITHIN    THESE FLIGHT INFORMATION REGIONS (FIR) DUE TO MILITARY ACTIVITIES AND    GNSS INTERFERENCE. THERE IS A POTENTIAL RISK TO AIRCRAFT AT ALL    ALTITUDES, INCLUDING OVERFLIGHTS AND THE ARRIVAL AND DEPARTURE PHASES    OF FLIGHT.        AIR NAVIGATION AND AIR TRAFFIC CONTROL SERVICES MAINTAIN THEIR    SURVEILLANCE SYSTEMS (SURVEILLANCE RADAR) AND CONVENTIONAL RADIO    NAVIGATION AIDS (VOR/DME) NATIONWIDE FULLY OPERATIONAL, AS THESE ARE    NOT VULNERABLE TO GNSS INTERFERENCE. F) SFC G) UNL CREATED: 16 MAR 2026 19:47 SOURCE: MMMXYNYX]]></description><Polygon><outerBoundaryIs><LinearRing><coordinates>0.161696,0.000000,0 0.160050,0.023012,0 0.155146,0.045555,0 0.147084,0.067171,0 0.136027,0.087419,0 0.122202,0.105888,0 0.105888,0.122202,0 0.087419,0.136027,0 0.067171,0.147084,0 0.045555,0.155146,0 0.023012,0.160050,0 0.000000,0.161696,0 -0.023012,0.160050,0 -0.045555,0.155146,0 -0.067171,0.147084,0 -0.087419,0.136027,0 -0.105888,0.122202,0 -0.122202,0.105888,0 -0.136027,0.087419,0 -0.147084,0.067171,0 -0.155146,0.045555,0 -0.160050,0.023012,0 -0.161696,0.000000,0 -0.160050,-0.023012,0 -0.155146,-0.045555,0 -0.147084,-0.067171,0 -0.136027,-0.087419,0 -0.122202,-0.105888,0 -0.105888,-0.122202,0 -0.087419,-0.136027,0 -0.067171,-0.147084,0 -0.045555,-0.155146,0 -0.023012,-0.160050,0 -0.000000,-0.161696,0 0.023012,-0.160050,0 0.045555,-0.155146,0 0.067171,-0.147084